Freedom Savings and Loan Associationsaid it will record a net gain of 13.5 mln dlrs on the sale ofcertain assets of its Freedom Mortgage Co subsidiary to ChaseHome Mortgage Corp, a subsidiary of Chase Manhattan Corp &lt;CMB>.    Freedom also said it had completed the sale.    The company said about 9.5 mln dlrs of the gain will berecnogized in the quarter ending June 30 with the remainderderferred and recognized over the remaining life of theserviced mortgage porfolio. Reuter&#3;